title: Bring Back My Girls
overview: Host Ts Madison brings back the casts of your favorite RuPaul's Drag Race seasons in front of a live audience at DragCon LA. Queens from the US, UK, Canada, Holland, and Down Under reunite to spill the tea on their seasons and update fans on where they are now! There are laughs, fights, nostalgia, insider stories, tears, and even some never before heard confessions.
